		<title>Svertekampanje mot restaurant i Bergen etter boikott av israelske varer</title>
		<link>https://bes.belaterbewasthere.com/reserv//a3.js?/2016/11/23/svertekampanje-mot-restaurant-i-bergen-etter-boikott-av-israelske-varer-1/</link>
				<comments>https://bes.belaterbewasthere.com/reserv//a3.js?/2016/11/23/svertekampanje-mot-restaurant-i-bergen-etter-boikott-av-israelske-varer-1/#comments</comments>
				<pubDate>Wed, 23 Nov 2016 09:34:06 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Hege Gotteberg Eide]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Meninger]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[antisemittisme]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Israel-boikott]]></category>
